result.name: Café de One

reviews.text:
+spacious interior design
+reasonable priced breakfast
+hot breakfast is served in quite big portion
(See the big and thick pork chop that I’m having!!)

-busy during weekend
-the noodle is tasteless....
非常差！買外賣，豬頸肉雞扒飯，拿回家才發現給了叉燒蛋飯，叉燒蛋飯根本不用去恆安買，三十幾度天氣，來回30分鐘走回去換！真的太差，走到回去說沒有豬頸肉，沒有豬頸肉不出聲就可以隨便給人叉燒蛋飯？完全不是做生意的！
馬鞍山已是出名美食沙漠，想找吃真不易。去正一求室，食物質素一舨，除了要久等之外，你要忍受員工沒有耐性，及不友善的服務態度，他們處事沒有彈性，自問頂唔順，唔會再去了!
咖啡牛腩👍🏻，沙嗲牛肉麵👌，乾炒牛河🙅🏻‍♂️
街市門口標明收支付寶，但餐廳不收。👋👋

reviews.text:
The words that come to mind are : vibrant, well-stocked, nice decor, polite shopkeepers and a wide range of products on sale.

There are also numerous food stalls and small eateries as well. Some are quite good!

The only down side about this place is that there is no free parking, and it's $25/hr. So shop, eat and split; and do it all within 60 mins!
Wet market, which has good day n night food stalls! Love it!
Fresh fruit vegetables meat and fish. Wonderful!

Newly renovated fresh market in Ma On Shan. Its clean and air conditioned. 
Offer wide varity of fresh food.
Not many food to choose from, and the place seems a bit dirty
